div.p:
nīnuṁ tr̥tīyajanmadoḷ vigaḷitasaṁsr̥tinigaḷaneyappeyembuduṁ;

      cāraṇayugaḷacaraṇayugaḷakke karakamaḷayugaḷamaṁ mugidu bīḻkoṇḍatitvaritagatiyiṁ

      baruttuṁ,

antu vajranābhi celviṅge nābhiyuṁ viḷāsakkāvāsamuṁ aḷaviṅge

      daḷamuṁ aṟiviṅge guṟiyuṁ kaḷege kulabhavanamuṁ pratāpakkaḍarpum āgi baḷevannegaṁ;

      vajrasēna mahārājaṁ ā kumāranoḷādondu yōgyatege santōṣambaṭṭu,
